lib-tdlib-android
=================

This repository is a verbatim redistribution of prebuilt binaries; it builds
nothing from source. It packages an Android AAR containing:

  * org.drinkless.tdlib.{TdApi,Client}  - the generated TDLib Java API
  * jniLibs/<abi>/libtdjni.so           - the TDLib JNI native library
  * jniLibs/<abi>/libsslx.so            - OpenSSL libssl (renamed to avoid conflicts)
  * jniLibs/<abi>/libcryptox.so         - OpenSSL libcrypto (renamed to avoid conflicts)

for four ABIs: arm64-v8a, armeabi-v7a, x86, x86_64.

Provenance
----------
The prebuilt artifacts are taken verbatim from the TGX-Android/tdlib project
(the official Telegram X TDLib prebuilt distribution):

  https://github.com/TGX-Android/tdlib
  Pinned commit: 63524bd14bebb9d7f9f04a1747675501ec41ea0a

Bump the mirror deliberately (re-copy the .so + TdApi.java/Client.java from a
newer TGX-Android/tdlib commit, tag a new release, re-verify) rather than
tracking upstream automatically, so builds stay reproducible.

